## Full System Architecture

```
DATA SOURCES
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   IoT Sensors          Drone Flights          Agronomy Docs
   (every 5 min)        (every few days)       (static + updated)
        │                     │                       │
        ▼                     ▼                       ▼
  ┌──────────┐        ┌──────────────┐        ┌──────────────┐
  │  MQTT /  │        │  Band Math   │        │  PDF/Text    │
  │  Kafka   │        │  Engine      │        │  Chunker     │
  └────┬─────┘        │  NDVI/NDRE   │        └──────┬───────┘
       │              └──────┬───────┘               │
       │                     │                       │
  ┌────▼─────┐    ┌──────────▼──────────┐            │
  │ Sliding  │    │ DroneContextBlock   │            │
  │ Window   │    │ (structured text)   │            │
  │ Extractor│    └──────────┬──────────┘            │
  └────┬─────┘               │ nightly               │
       │                  RAPTOR ◄────────────────────┘
  ┌────▼──────────┐       Tree Build
  │ SensorContext │       (UMAP + GMM + FAISS index)
  │ Block (live)  │
  └────┬──────────┘

QUERY TIME PIPELINE
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  User Query
      │
      ▼
  Query Rewriter          ← conversation history via rolling summary
      │
      ▼
  HyDE Expander           ← LLM generates hypothetical agronomic answer
      │                      to bridge lay language → technical terms
      ▼
  FAISS Search            ← retrieve top-N candidates from KB
      │
      ▼
  ColBERT Reranker        ← token-level rerank to top-K
      │
      ▼
  RAPTOR Build            ← cluster + summarize to N-level hierarchy
  (on retrieved docs)        built fresh per query for precision
      │
      ▼
  ┌────────────────────────────────────┐
  │         PLANNER (ReWOO)           │
  │  - Sees: query + RAPTOR tree      │
  │  - Sees: data availability meta   │
  │    (sensor freshness, last flight)│
  │  - Outputs:                       │
  │    1. Sub-queries (#E1, #E2, ...) │
  │    2. Context Priority Blueprint  │
  │       PRIMARY / SECONDARY /       │
  │       TERTIARY for each source    │
  └────────────┬───────────────────────┘
               │
               ▼
  ┌────────────────────────────────────┐
  │           WORKER (ReWOO)          │
  │  Executes each plan step:         │
  │  - Raptor[query] → RAPTOR search  │
  │  - LLM[context] → reasoning step  │
  │  Fills #E1, #E2, ... with results │
  └────────────┬───────────────────────┘
               │
               ▼
  ┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │              CONTEXT ASSEMBLER                        │
  │                                                       │
  │  Reads Priority Blueprint from Planner                │
  │  Assembles final context block in priority order:     │
  │                                                       │
  │  PRIMARY:   [SensorContextBlock]  ← live data        │
  │  SECONDARY: [RAPTOR Evidence]     ← retrieved KB     │
  │  TERTIARY:  [DroneContextBlock]   ← last flight      │
  │                                                       │
  │  Tagged with metadata (freshness, source, confidence) │
  └────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────────┘
               │
               ▼
  ┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │                    SOLVER LLM                         │
  │                                                       │
  │  Phase 1: groq/llama-3.1-8b-instant                  │
  │  Phase 2: groq/llama-3.1-70b-versatile (solver only) │
  │  Phase 3: vLLM on NRP → LoRA fine-tuned Llama-3.1-8B │
  │           on agricultural QA datasets                  │
  │                                                       │
  │  Prompt structure:                                    │
  │  "Answer using PRIMARY evidence most. Use SECONDARY   │
  │   for thresholds. TERTIARY provides spatial context.  │
  │   Cite evidence. Quantify recommendations."           │
  └────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────────┘
               │
               ▼
         Final Answer
  (cited, quantified, source-attributed)
